メソッドの詳細

getProvider

public static MessagingProvider getProvider(java.lang.String messagingType,
                                            byte[] messageSignature)
                                     throws java.security.NoSuchProviderException
Return a messaging provider associated to the given name. The name should be one of the following names: "TCP", "UDP" or "Emulator". There is an utility class Signature to generate a signature.

パラメータ:
messagingType - name of a messaging provider.
messageSignature - signature embedded to every message.
戻り値:
a message provider.
例外:
java.security.NoSuchProviderException

forceEmulator

public static void forceEmulator(int initialEmulatorHostID)
Enforce returning the emulator provider on the factory.

パラメータ:
initialEmulatorHostID - the first ID of virtual host names (emuXX) in an emulator.
